<plot>The 2005 edition of the annual Bodil Awards awarded top honours for best Danish picture to _Kongekabale (2004)_ (qv), while the four acting awards went one each to Kongekabale, _Forbrydelser (2004)_ (qv), _Brødre (2004)_ (qv) and _Pusher II (2004)_ (qv). _Tintin et moi (2003)_ (qv) was named best documentary. Hosted by 'Michael Carøe' (qv), the show also saw the international awards go to _Comme une image (2004)_ (qv) and _Lost in Translation (2003)_ (qv) while 'Morten Søborg' (qv) won a diploma for cinematography and 'Janus Billeskov Jansen' (qv) received the honorary Bodil.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?077580</url></doc>
